ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: An overview of American Economic History. Definitely worth taking for anyone interested in applied fields (whether micro or macro).
good. I would definitely recommend it to others
I would strong recommend since it gives a good idea of what is the economic history.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Since I am interested in Economic History/Political Economy/Development, this course has been very helpful in generating research questions and introducing me to the literature.
Yes, it deepen my understanding about economic development

It gives me the opportunity to use all my economic background in the historical analysis. I don't think I will deal with economic history but it improve my ability of critically analyzing economic papers.
